1. *Čitam* knjigu o istoriji Srbije. (I am reading a book about the history of Serbia.)
2. *Čitala* sam to već nekoliko puta. (I have already read it several times.)
3. *Čitao* sam istoriju na fakultetu. (I studied history at the university.)
4. Ona *čita* njegovu knjigu. (She is reading his book.)
5. Moja sestra *čitaju* knjige svaki dan. (My sister reads books every day.)
6. *Čitati* ću to uveče. (I will read it in the evening.)